{"type": "article", "id": 9944, "title": "Raphia 骑行防汗耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-25T08:02:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110938Fu4nLkcW68SzGHEC.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t丹麦科技公司 Bang And Olufsen 为英国自行车品牌 Raphia 推出了一款新的骑行防汗耳机，使得骑行者可以更加舒适地享受音乐。这款耳机的设计灵感来自于其经典款的 “Play H6” 耳机，耳罩采取非洲毛羊皮制成，而其他部分则采用皮革材料——整个耳机见不到塑料的影子。颜色上有黑色和天然浅皮革两种颜色。耳机目前售价 399 英镑，在 Raphia 专卖店和 Bang And Olufsen 门店都可以买到。<a href=\"http://beoplay.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110934OBWDHwEp0Tv9N3MK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85085575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110934bsPmKhVYijGuqozS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110935lL5tzyKSJsbWmfIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110935hzW8YZ3mCdTeHyQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110936XvDVs0wSLzmxY1FI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021109368MYRH7DoGzVgdNyP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021109374VnHuNaTefXW0L2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}